{"tid":972801,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【獲獎不斷】球皇摩迪擊敗祖高域再獲一大獎","createTime":"2019-01-07T15:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T15:59:03.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30104a801b4188d66640a3ebba82ed3ce3b0dd7b","tid":972801,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"2018年對摩迪而言，無疑是成功的一年，他獲得不少獎項。<br />\n<br />\n　　據《天空體育》的報導，摩迪擊敗祖高域，收穫一個新的獎項：巴爾幹年度最佳運動員。<br />\n<br />\n在這個獎項排名第二的是網球名將祖高域，女子網球名將賀拿普位列第三。<br />\n<br />\n　　摩迪在2018年跟隨皇馬贏得歐聯冠軍，帶領克羅地亞晉級世界盃決賽，他也被評為世界盃MVP。摩迪今年還收穫了金球獎、歐洲賽季最佳球員以及FIFA年度最佳球員等獎項。"},{"pid":"a3d6b8623bf52997897baa20a73aa57f69993cf6","tid":972801,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b807456bae8ebddfca48a49b9eca1f3959f314af","tid":972801,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"摩迪帶領皇馬3奪歐聯<br />\n幫克軍入世界盃決賽<br />\n仲拎世界盃mvp<br />\n<br />\n實至名歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355186fbbc9c4c4e1bab34ce62c58ceaf0cd758a","tid":972801,"uid":97212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b807456bae8ebddfca48a49b9eca1f3959f314af","tid":972801,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"摩迪帶領皇馬3奪歐聯<br />\n幫克軍入世界盃決賽<br />\n仲拎世界盃mvp<br />\n<br />\n實至名歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"下年去埋挑戰歐霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}